sourcesContent: import React from "react"; import { bool } from "prop-types"; import { StyledMenu } from "./Menu.styled"; import LogoContainer from '../LogoContainer/LogoContainer' import LogoIcon from '../../../icons/LogoIcon' const Menu = ({ signedIn, open }) => { return ( <> {signedIn ? artists music submit music about contact : !signedIn ? home about login/signup : null } ); }; Menu.propTypes = { open: bool.isRequired, signedIn: bool.isRequired }; export default Menu;
